---
import Heading from './Heading.astro';
import Button from './Button.astro';

export interface Props {
  class?: string;
}

const { class: className = '' } = Astro.props;
---

<section class={`py-20 bg-white ${className}`}>
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <!-- Artist Image -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="aspect-[4/5] bg-blue-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <!-- Placeholder for artist image -->
          <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-300 to-blue-400 flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-blue-700 text-lg">Foto de Karli</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Decorative element -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-blue-600 rounded-lg opacity-20"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Artist Info -->
      <div>
        <Heading level={2} class="mb-6">
          Karli
          <span class="block text-lg font-normal text-gray-600 mt-2">
            Maestra del Fine Line y Minimalismo
          </span>
        </Heading>

        <div class="prose prose-lg mb-8">
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Karli se especializa en el delicado arte del fine line y los diseños minimalistas. 
            Su precisión y elegancia en cada trazo la han convertido en la artista preferida 
            para quienes buscan tatuajes sutiles pero impactantes.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
            Con un background en arquitectura y 5 años de experiencia en tatuaje, 
            Karli aporta una perspectiva única al estudio, creando diseños geométricos 
            y orgánicos de extraordinaria belleza.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Specialties -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Especialidades:</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm">Fine Line</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm">Minimalista</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm">Geométrico</span>
            <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm">Floral</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Portfolio Preview -->
        <div class="mb-8">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Trabajos Destacados:</h3>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-2">
            <div class="aspect-square bg-blue-200 rounded-lg"></div>
            <div class="aspect-square bg-blue-200 rounded-lg"></div>
            <div class="aspect-square bg-blue-200 rounded-lg"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA Button -->
        <Button 
          href="/booking?artist=karli" 
          variant="primary" 
          size="lg"
          class="bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-700 border-none"
        >
          Reservar con Karli
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
